ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2010-11
PrecisAppointment of PERRY CALDERWOOD as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Senegal; HILARY CHILDS-ADAMS as Ambassador of Canada to the Lebanese Republic; MARK GWOZDECKY as Ambassador of Canada to the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan; JAMAL KHOKHAR as Ambassador of Canada to the Federative Republic of Brazil; GWYNETH KUTZ as Ambassador of Canada to the Argentine Republic; and MICHAEL SMALL as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of Australia with concurrent accreditation to the Solomon Islands and as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Palau and the Republic of the Marshall Islands.
